@startuml
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Web UI / App" as UI
participant "Words API" as API
participant "Payment Gateway" as Payment
participant "Email Service" as Email
database "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Нажать "Купить колоду"
activate UI
UI -> API: Инициировать покупку (deck_id)
activate API

API -> DB: Создать заказ (статус: PENDING)
activate DB
DB --> API: order_id
deactivate DB

API -> Payment: Charge(card_details, amount, order_id)
activate Payment
Payment --> API: payment_id, status: SUCCESS
deactivate Payment

API -> DB: Обновить статус заказа (CONFIRMED)
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API -> DB: Добавить колоду (deck_id) пользователю (user_id)
activate DB
DB --> API: OK
deactivate DB

API ->> Email: [Асинхронно] SendReceipt(user_email, order_id)
activate Email
Email --> API: OK (в очереди)
deactivate Email

API --> UI: 200 OK, purchase_successful
deactivate API

UI --> User: Показать экран "Колода добавлена!"
deactivate UI

@enduml